Losing your bag is the worst because airlines always try to blame you for it. I once went to file a claim for lost luggage, and they said it would arrive in a few days. Nothing. I called them and they said I never filed the claim. Then they said I had to do it online, which I did that second. Then they said it would arrive within a few days but again, nothing. I finally got a call from a random warehouse across the world saying they have my bag, the airline never claimed it!!! Thankfully the nice lady got it to me the very next day! Make sure you always have your contact information on your bags while traveling, folks!
